  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/cb7f6b6dcfb512d4adedfa830bdd2f08.poster.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=97 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/cb7f6b6dcfb512d4adedfa830bdd2f08.webm?t=1773747556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>Occupy White Walls</i>, you can create a museum and curate its contents. Construct a space, fill it with art that is personal to you, and open its doors to welcome the world! OWW is powered by a first-of-its-kind art discovery AI called DAISY and has a fun, creative, and grown-up player community. (just don’t call it ‘Hipster Minecraft’ )<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/6eb649ff5c763d494435f1f01efd29bd.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=1919 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/0386453a00e7a4d2c79bc34ea4f96d1b.poster.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=97 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/0386453a00e7a4d2c79bc34ea4f96d1b.webm?t=1773747556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Build </strong>in a creative sandbox environment with thousands of unique assets. There is no limit to your creativity.<br></li><li><strong> Custom Music</strong> Include your own music and share it with others<br></li><li><strong>A grownup community</strong> with entertaining and inspiring personalities<br></li><li><strong>Explore </strong>tens of thousands of inspiring, creative spaces created by players<br></li><li><strong>Collaborative building</strong> - Build with friends (or strangers)<br></li><li><strong>Pixel Art Galore</strong> - Get creative and create custom art with interactive mosaics<br></li><li><strong>DAISY, a groundbreaking art discovery AI</strong>- Discover art you never knew you'd like without needing any prior art knowledge<br></li><li><strong>MAISY</strong>(DAISY's little sister)- an AI to help you find similar artworks<br></li><li><strong>Discover </strong>artworks from historical masters like Monet to artworks from a vast array of contemporary artists from an ever-growing database of tens of thousands of artworks.<br></li><li><strong>OWW for artists</strong> - Upload your art into the game and discover new audiences using the power of DAISY, AI. Kultura <br></li><li>Visit the Plaza and see what strange new assets Larry and Peggy offer daily</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/0dbfa4c7ce3bcac5b3912223f26a9dd9.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/b6d28e1bc6cc2b982d1e8f5a097b9968.poster.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=97 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/b6d28e1bc6cc2b982d1e8f5a097b9968.webm?t=1773747556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/cb7f6b6dcfb512d4adedfa830bdd2f08.poster.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=97 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/cb7f6b6dcfb512d4adedfa830bdd2f08.webm?t=1773747556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In <i>Occupy White Walls</i>, you can create a museum and curate its contents. Construct a space, fill it with art that is personal to you, and open its doors to welcome the world! OWW is powered by a first-of-its-kind art discovery AI called DAISY and has a fun, creative, and grown-up player community. (just don’t call it ‘Hipster Minecraft’ )<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/6eb649ff5c763d494435f1f01efd29bd.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=1919 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/0386453a00e7a4d2c79bc34ea4f96d1b.poster.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=97 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/0386453a00e7a4d2c79bc34ea4f96d1b.webm?t=1773747556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Build </strong>in a creative sandbox environment with thousands of unique assets. There is no limit to your creativity.<br></li><li><strong> Custom Music</strong> Include your own music and share it with others<br></li><li><strong>A grownup community</strong> with entertaining and inspiring personalities<br></li><li><strong>Explore </strong>tens of thousands of inspiring, creative spaces created by players<br></li><li><strong>Collaborative building</strong> - Build with friends (or strangers)<br></li><li><strong>Pixel Art Galore</strong> - Get creative and create custom art with interactive mosaics<br></li><li><strong>DAISY, a groundbreaking art discovery AI</strong>- Discover art you never knew you'd like without needing any prior art knowledge<br></li><li><strong>MAISY</strong>(DAISY's little sister)- an AI to help you find similar artworks<br></li><li><strong>Discover </strong>artworks from historical masters like Monet to artworks from a vast array of contemporary artists from an ever-growing database of tens of thousands of artworks.<br></li><li><strong>OWW for artists</strong> - Upload your art into the game and discover new audiences using the power of DAISY, AI. Kultura <br></li><li>Visit the Plaza and see what strange new assets Larry and Peggy offer daily</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/0dbfa4c7ce3bcac5b3912223f26a9dd9.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=400 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/b6d28e1bc6cc2b982d1e8f5a097b9968.poster.avif?t=1773747556\" width=616 height=97 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876160/extras/b6d28e1bc6cc2b982d1e8f5a097b9968.webm?t=1773747556\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>",
